### SECTION 1 — ENVIRONMENT & SECRETS
# ⚠️ NEVER remove entries from this section.
# If you think you need to commit a secret, you are wrong.
# Use Google Secret Manager instead.
.env
.env.local
.env.development
.env.production
.env.test
.env.*.local
!/.env.example

*-key.json
*-credentials.json
*-service-account.json
google-services.json
GoogleService-Info.plist
# GCP service account and ADC files
service-account*.json
application_default_credentials.json
gcloud-service-key.json

*.tfstate
*.tfstate.backup
.terraform/

*secret*
*credential*
*private-key*
credentials/
!credentials/*.placeholder.json


